    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A thick, sticky liquid, usually one consisting of a concentrated solution of sugar in water or other medium such as the juices of fruits. Used as food, in cookery, or as a medium for medication.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
